/blog               /journal                       301
/blog/*             /journal                       301

# Old enquiry endpoints -> Enquiry page
/enquiries          /enquiry                       301
/enquiries/create   /enquiry                       301
/enquiries/*        /enquiry                       301

# Old tailored / bespoke -> Custom tour  (wildcard is safe here)
